## 📚 実装アルゴリズム一覧

| カテゴリ | クラス | 論文 |
|---------|--------|------|
| CART | `CARTClassifier`, `CARTRegressor` | Breiman et al. (1984) |
| Random Forest | `RandomForestClassifier`, `RandomForestRegressor` | Breiman (2001) |
| Extra Trees | `ExtraTreesClassifier`, `ExtraTreesRegressor` | Geurts et al. (2006) |
| 正則化 | `VariablePenaltyForest`, `LeafWeightRegularizedForest` | カスタム実装 |
| 制約 | `MonotonicConstrainedForest`, `LinearConstrainedForest` | カスタム実装 |
| 斜め分割 | `ObliqueForest` | Murthy et al. (1994) |
| Rotation Forest | `RotationForest`, `RandomRotationForest` | Rodriguez et al. (2006) |
| SPORF | `SPORFClassifier`, `SPORFRegressor` | Tomita et al. (2020) JMLR |
| RGF | `RegularizedGreedyForest` | Johnson & Zhang (2014) |
| ソフト決定木 | `SoftDecisionTree`, `SoftDecisionForest` | Frosst & Hinton (2017) |
| Linear Tree | `LinearTree`, `LinearForest`, `LinearBoost` | Potts & Sammut (2005) |
| RuleFit | `RuleFit` | Friedman & Popescu (2008) |
| Bernoulli RF | `BernoulliRandomForest` | Denil et al. (2014) |
| GRF | `GeneralizedRandomForest`, `QuantileForest`, `CausalForest` | Athey et al. (2019) |
| Kernel Forest | `RandomKernelForest` | Ustimenko & Prokhorenkova (2022) |
| 異常検知 | `IsolationForest` | Liu et al. (2008) |
| 分位回帰 | `QuantileRegressionForest` | Meinshausen (2006) |
| 生存分析 | `RandomSurvivalForest` | Ishwaran et al. (2008) |
| オンライン学習 | `MondrianForest` | Lakshminarayanan et al. (2014) |
| 類似度 | `RFSimilarity`, `RFKernel` | Breiman (2001) §8 |
| **総合クラス** | **`ForestBuilder`** | — |

